Enum Class MessageHeader

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<MessageHeader>
it.polimi.ingsw.connection.MessageHeader
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<MessageHeader>, Constable
public enum MessageHeader extends Enum<MessageHeader>
The MessageHeader enum represents the headers for different types of messages. These headers are used to identify the purpose or type of a message.
